Newspaper Example

set.seed(498)
N <- 1000
D <- 50 + sample.int(50, N, replace=TRUE)
plot(1:N, D, xlab="day", ylab="demand")

p <- 1
c <- 0.25
theta <- numeric(N+1)
theta[1] <- 50
alpha <- 0.5
reward <- numeric(N)

for (i in 1:N) {
  reward[i] <- p*min(theta[i], D[i]) - c*theta[i]
  drdt <- ifelse(theta[i] < D[i], p-c, -c)
  theta[i+1] <- theta[i] + alpha*drdt
}
par(mfrow=c(2,1), mar=c(1,4,1,1))
ylim=c(0,100)
plot(1:N, D, xlab="day", ylab="demand", ylim=ylim, col="gray", cex=0.25)
lines(1:N, theta[1:N], type="l", col="blue", lwd=2)
plot(1:N, reward, type="l", xlab="day", ylab="reward")
